                  <td width="560" valign="top" bgcolor="#C4EECE" class="style2"><p class="style79"><strong><em>Every month another crop:</em></strong><em>&nbsp; The formation of new consortia continued  apace in the first quarter, with new entrants in a broad array of unrelated  disciplines, including&nbsp; power over the  Ethernet, open source geodata, storage, and manufacturing and process automation  &ndash; providing an example of how varied the areas of technology collaboration  continue to be.</em></p></td>
