                  <td width="455" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" class="style2"><p>Tim Berners-Lee,  challenging Britain to release ordinance data<a href="http://technology.guardian.co.uk/weekly/story/0,,1736751,00.html">...Full Story</a></p></td>
                </tr>
